    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. It's been my pride and joy\u2014always reliable and such a blast to drive on weekend getaways. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has that wonderful personality you only get from a car that's been truly loved. There might be a tiny mark here or there if you look close, but it still looks stunning in the driveway and runs like a dream. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and you can take it for a spin!",
