    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 V8\u2014the last of the naturally aspirated M-power engines. This example has been treated to comprehensive preventative maintenance, including upgraded ACL rod bearings and ARP bolts to ensure bottom-end resilience. The DCT transmission has been serviced with fresh Pentosin fluid and high-flow filters, providing lightning-fast shifts. I've also addressed the common throttle actuator failure points with upgraded gears. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and a precise alignment tailored for spirited cornering. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a high-performance driver, the mechanical synchronization and thermal management are flawless. This is a turn-key apex hunter for the discerning enthusiast who understands the value of a properly maintained S65 block.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs perfect. Clean title. Cold AC. Maintenance up to date. Priced to move today. No games. First cash takes it.",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine yourself behind the wheel as the sun dips below the horizon, the engine\u2019s rhythmic hum a perfect harmony to the crashing waves. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine crafted for the open road. With its sun-kissed paint and the rich aroma of aged leather, every mile feels like a chapter in a classic novel. It bears the graceful marks of a life spent chasing horizons, offering a raw, mechanical connection that modern machines have long forgotten. This roadster doesn't just drive\u2014it breathes, waiting for its next great navigator to take the helm and write the next adventure.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the perfect balance of performance and value with this meticulously maintained vehicle. Representing a standout example in its class, this car features a documented service history and has passed a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for reliability and safety. The interior remains remarkably fresh, complemented by an exterior that retains a sharp, professional presence. This is a turn-key opportunity for a discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that delivers a premium driving experience.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s got soul and has been treated like one of the family, you\u2019ve found it. This beauty has been my pride and joy\u2014she runs smooth, looks sharp, and has that perfect 'get up and go' that makes every drive a treat. She\u2019s got a few tiny badges of honor from the road, but that just shows she's been truly enjoyed! I\u2019ve kept her well-maintained and she's ready to find a new home where she'll be just as loved. Come by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I'm so excited about this one!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
