      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused specimen that has been treated with extreme mechanical sympathy. This S54 powerplant remains exceptionally healthy, delivering a linear torque curve and that signature metallic rasp through the upper RPM range. The VANOS unit is quiet, and the subframe\u2014a critical point on these chassis\u2014has been professionally inspected and reinforced for long-term peace of mind. I\u2019ve optimized the cooling system with a high-flow aluminum radiator to ensure thermal stability during spirited sessions. The steering rack is precise with zero dead zone, and the suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings to sharpen turn-in response. This is a turn-key performance machine for the enthusiast who values mechanical integrity and a sorted drivetrain over garage queen status.",
